abstract: Nausheen Rahman of Staten Island is charged with murder after infant is found dead in trash can at her home.
lead_paragraph: The police said Nausheen Rahman, 28, was also charged with concealing a corpse after the baby was discovered in a trash can in the New Springville neighborhood.

headline.main: Staten Island Woman Charged With Murder After Infant Is Found Dead
headline.print_headline: Baby’s Death Yields Charge of Murder
